-molecuar\ninteractions apparently play a subordinate role, suggest a rather generic\nnature of the process of structural relaxation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Mar 2021 18:27:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-15"}
