 $0\\le w_{re} \\le 1$.\nHowever, for exponential potential with power-law kinetic term, the equation of\nstate during reheating $w_{re}$ should be greater than $1$ for $r-n_s$\npredictions to lie within $68\\%$C.L. of joint constraints on $n_s$ and $r$ from\nPlanck-2018 observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Mar 2021 15:09:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 16:21:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Sep 2021 08:03:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
